as the deep sea♪

685
00:42:08,290 --> 00:42:10,750
♪From afar♪

686
00:42:12,700 --> 00:42:15,850
♪It once lit up dreams with a breath♪

687
00:42:16,770 --> 00:42:19,880
♪But vanished with a sigh♪

688
00:42:21,100 --> 00:42:24,470
♪Brushing past my fingertips♪

689
00:42:24,870 --> 00:42:28,240
♪My heartstrings were stirred quietly♪

690
00:42:29,070 --> 00:42:31,010
♪As if we once met before♪

691
