♪Leaving only obsessions♪

694
00:42:46,260 --> 00:42:49,660
♪I've wandered in the world♪

695
00:42:50,160 --> 00:42:53,160
♪Yet cannot have it all♪

696
00:42:54,720 --> 00:42:57,990
♪We meet and part in the fires of war♪

697
00:42:58,310 --> 00:43:02,000
♪Embracing,
leaving tender marks of love♪

698
00:43:02,700 --> 00:43:04,630
♪With one breathtaking glance♪

699
00:43:05,170 --> 00:43:10,090
♪How could I ever forget♪

700
00:43:10,670 --> 00:43:12,950
♪I would cross mountains and seas♪

701
00:43:12,950 --> 00:43:15,470
♪To spend time with you♪

702
00:43:15,720 --> 00:43:17,080
♪When we grow old♪

703
00:43:17,080 --> 00:43:19,670
♪Nothing will change♪

704
00:43:19,670 --> 00:43:21,270
♪The misty rains never cease♪

705
00:43:21,270 --> 00:43:24,130
♪Falling gently on your brow♪

706
00:43:24,130 --> 00:43:28,120
♪Lingering in my heart♪

707
00:43:28,120 --> 00:43:29,820
♪I would sever fate's ties♪

708
00:43:29,820 --> 00:43:32,240
♪To protect your smiling eyes♪

709
00:43:32,630 --> 00:43:36,500
♪Even if behind me lies a storm♪

710
00:43:36,500 --> 00:43:37,610
♪No matter the trials♪

